                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Global talent:</strong> Our US and Sri Lanka teams provide
                  world-class expertise at efficient rates
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Automation at scale:</strong> AI handles repetitive tasks,
                  freeing humans for strategic thinking
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Smart technology stack:</strong> We use the best AI tools
