                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Proven processes:</strong> 25 years of experience means
                  we know exactly what works
                </li>
              </ul>
              <p>
                The result? You get the firepower of a 10-person marketing team
                for the cost of one employee - without sacrificing quality.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">
              <span>Are there additional fees?</span>
              <svg
                class="faq-icon"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>
                It depends on what systems you want to integrate with.
                Third-party systems or existing apps are sometimes better to
                utilize as they have more users or a bigger established base.
                These external platforms may have their own subscription fees,
                but we'll work with you to choose the most cost-effective
                solutions that deliver the best results for your business.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Services & Capabilities -->
        <div class="faq-category">
          <h3 class="category-title">Services & Capabilities</h3>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">
              <span>What exactly do you do?</span>
              <svg
                class="faq-icon"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>
                We're your complete AI-powered marketing department. Our
                services include:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>Marketing Strategy:</strong> Comprehensive planning and
                  campaign management
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>AI Development:</strong> Custom AI implementations and automation
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Website Development:</strong> Design, development, and optimization
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>SEO & Local Search:</strong> Organic visibility and local
