                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">
              <span
                >What makes you different from other marketing agencies?</span
              >
              <svg
                class="faq-icon"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>
                We're not just marketers - we're AI experts with deep technical
                knowledge:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>5+ years of AI mastery:</strong> We've been working with
