                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>You own everything:</strong> All accounts, code, content,
                  and data belong to you
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Human-centric AI:</strong> We use AI to amplify human creativity,
                  not replace it
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Proven results:</strong> 3.8x average ROAS, 259% revenue
                  growth for clients
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">
              <span>Do you work with businesses in my industry?</span>
              <svg
                class="faq-icon"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>
                We've successfully helped businesses across many industries
                including:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  Professional Services (law firms, consultants, financial
                  advisors)
                </li>
                <li>Real Estate (developers, agents, property management)</li>
                <li>Healthcare (practices, clinics, medical devices)</li>
                <li>B2B Services (SaaS, technology, consulting)</li>
