              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">
              <span>What AI tools and platforms do you use?</span>
              <svg
                class="faq-icon"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="20"
