                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>We're masters of all major AI platforms:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>Generative AI:</strong> ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>AI Content:</strong> Midjourney, DALL-E, Runway ML, ElevenLabs
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>AI Marketing:</strong> Smartly.io, Pattern89, Mutiny, Drift
