                </li>
              </ul>
              <p>
                We stay on top of every new AI platform and capability, testing
                new tools as they launch.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Process & Timeline -->
        <div class="faq-category">
          <h3 class="category-title">Process & Timeline</h3>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">
              <span>How long does it take to see results?</span>
              <svg
                class="faq-icon"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>Timeline varies by service and goals:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>Paid Advertising:</strong> Initial results within 2-4 weeks,
                  optimization ongoing
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Website Launch:</strong> New sites typically launch within
                  2-6 weeks
                </li>
