              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">
              <span>What's the onboarding process like?</span>
              <svg
                class="faq-icon"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </button>
