            <button class="faq-question">
              <span>How involved do I need to be?</span>
              <svg
                class="faq-icon"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>We handle the heavy lifting, but your input is valuable:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>Initial setup (Week 1-2):</strong> 2-4 hours for discovery,
                  approvals, and account access
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Ongoing (Monthly):</strong> 1-2 hours for strategy reviews
